title: Cool Tribal Watch Face
summary: Tribal elements flow along your watchface!
description: This watch face has tribal elements that you will love.  Enjoy cool tribal shapes flowing on your watchface.The watch tells time, displays a verbose date and shows the remaining battery level for the smart watch.This app is compatible with all smartwatches that run android.When downloading this app, be aware that it takes some time for the watch face to appear in your android wear application.Visit http://osthoro.wix.com/osthoro for all available watchfaces or search osthoro in the app store.
descriptionHTML:
This watch face has tribal elements that you will love. Enjoy cool tribal shapes flowing on your watchface.
The watch tells time, displays a verbose date and shows the remaining battery level for the smart watch.
This app is compatible with all smartwatches that run android.

When downloading this app, be aware that it takes some time for the watch face to appear in your android wear application.

Visit http://osthoro.wix.com/osthoro for all available watchfaces or search osthoro in the app store.
